author: enridaga
msg: Main changes have been around the ReasoningServiceExecutor class, in order to prepare it to be an imlementation of Callable to be given to the JobManager.
* Removed references to JAX-RS types from ReasoningServiceExecutor
** ReasoningServiceResult, to be processed by the JAX-RS resource. In perspective this would be the outcome of the job (Callable<ReasoningServiceResult>)
** ResponseTaskBuilder, this class compute the JAX-RX response Object with data from a ReasoningServiceBuilder.
These two classes whould be moved to the api, later
